Subject: [PATCH v2 1/4] regulator: lp87565: enable voltage regardless of ENx pin
Date:   Wed, 17 Jun 2020 15:11:42 +0200
Message-Id: <20200617131145.15696-2-luca@lucaceresoli.net>
